data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch style home that sits on 2 acres and is nestled in the trees. This spacious home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing plenty of space for comfortable living.Outside you will find plenty of space to store your ATV, tractor etc. Sit on the back porch and enjoy the peace and quiet that country living offers. Whether you're looking for a peaceful retreat or a place to entertain family and friends, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and relaxation.
